{"type":null,"faqId":33497,"title":"情景智能是什么？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.39375in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">情景智能可以通过您的订单短信，帮助您管理航班、高铁、会议、酒店等预定信息，并在适当的时间及时提醒；还能根据联系人的生日信息，提醒您及时为亲朋好友送上生日祝福；情景智能通过学习您的上下班习惯，适时提供路况信息，祝您出行；</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">情景智能还能助您量化自我：1）活动总结，如步数、距离、卡路里等数据，并且如果活动量太小，提醒用户适当运动；2）使用手机娱乐时间统计，并分类：如社交、游戏、阅读等，如果每天使用手机时间累计超过一定时间，比如5小时，提醒用户多投入现实生活； 3）睡眠时间统计，睡眠不够或作息不健康时提醒用户；</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":143,"faqType":"系统功能与设置","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8217","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-System-Settings","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748629000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":49,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"情景智能","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}